dc_description_s: Two parts of the map (top/bottom) from Salem/Cumberland line to the Maurice River and the Maurice River to the Cumberland/Cape May line.|Map shows the grants and leases. The Creeks and rivers are drawn. There is a map of Bridgeton in more detail. Labeled creeks and rivers are Middle Marsh Creek, Cohansey Creek, Back Creek, Drumbo Creek, Cedar Creek, Nantuxant Creek, Fortescue Creek, Broad Oyster Creek, Fishing Creek, Straight Creek, Maurice River, and Dividing Creek
